OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPrison officers 'voting    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith their feet' amid jobs 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsurge                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Prisons are facing difficulties        
OL,6, recruiting enough officers amid a surge
OL,7, in job vacancies, a union has said.    
OL,9,FThis comes as job adverts have soared  
OL,10,Fto a record high in the run-up to      
OL,11,FChristmas, according to recruiters.    
OL,13,FDriving instructors, prison officers   
OL,14,Fand forklift truck drivers are amongst 
OL,15,Fthe jobs in highest demand, the        
OL,16,FRecruitment and Employment             
OL,17,FConfederation (REC) said.              
OL,19,FMeanwhile demand for construction roles
OL,20,Fdropped due to supply chain problems.  
